_sText:
Well here is my Osama hideout map. It's not done yet, there are still some bugs/glitches that need to be fixed.

The main building was made from blueprints so it is as close to the real thing as you can get without going in the actual building!

Don't close any double doors (opening them is safe) the game will crash lol a small bug I have to fix ;) 
If you forget and try to close one you'll have to end hl2.exe :(
